### Fizik Sistemi
```lua
-- Fizik body oluÅŸtur
local body = physics_body(player, {
    type = "dynamic",
    gravity_scale = 1.0,
    fixed_rotation = true
})

-- HÄ±z ayarla
physics_set_velocity(body, 100, 0)

-- Kuvvet uygula
apply_force(body, 0, -500)
apply_impulse(body, 0, 200)

-- Ã‡arpÄ±ÅŸma callback
on_begin_contact("player", "enemy", function()
    print("Player enemy ile Ã§arpÄ±ÅŸtÄ±!")
end)
```

### Tilemap
